.. _fts-sort-eg-uuid:

Sort by UUID
~~~~~~~~~~~~

The following query searches for the term ``hello`` in field ``b`` in
the ``users`` collection. The query sorts the results by field ``a``,
which contains polymorphic data (to demonstrate the sort order), in
ascending order.

